37202>>>>>                    Send Clear of hoUserDD
37203>>>>>                End
37203>>>>>>
37203>>>>>            End
37203>>>>>>
37203>>>>>            Else Begin
37204>>>>>                // This is added to delay latency to avoid hackers finding out whether the user exists or not.
37204>>>>>                Get CreatePasswordHash "This is to delay the response latency." (&sPassword) to iErr
37205>>>>>            End
37205>>>>>>
37205>>>>>        End
37205>>>>>>
